CLUB_ID= the funny lil numbers that appear behind https://uma.moe/circles/ when you are on your clubs page
GOAL_METRIC= the number of fans to gain for the month
DISCORD_WEBHOOK_URL= the discord webhook url (automatically gives you a copy url button when u make the webhook)
WEBHOOK_NAME= the name the "account" sending the messages in your server will have
CLUB_NAME= variable for the message so it names your club
